title: Conquer Your Campus
description:
I was very surprised to see that these eBooks from conqueryourcampus.com hadn&#039;t made it onto the torrent sites yet. I bought them a while back, so I figured I should share them for sure.

The basic premise is that all the usual "PUA" (pick-up artist) techniques don&#039;t really work well in college, where the game is completely different. These eBooks focus on those differences, and the techniques to succeed in the dating/relationship/etc. game at college. To see the whole sales pitch, check out the original website at conqueryourcampus.com; then come back here to avoid paying $37 ^_^.
